{"tid":2060863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三文四语：祖国强大了，你什么都不是","createTime":"2020-06-12T03:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T03:32:42.000Z","uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6566482193d0249d7642d70f60c2bff96bee8873","tid":2060863,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EaR4KEyU0AESIe8?format=jpg&amp;name=900x900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEaR4KEyU0AESIe8%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D900x900&h=799f31dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n满文解析： si / simbe (you), gurun (country), mafa (grandpa), mafari gurun (home country), A ofi (because of A), iliha (stood up), niak&ucirc;rahabi (to have knelt), etuhun (powerful), aitubume muterak&ucirc; (to be unable to rescue), yaya we (anyone), waka (not to be), bifi (having got)"},{"pid":"5eb13a24413ffb34722c13fcc2e01d33dd53b193","tid":2060863,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"是四文三语，满洲语同时用传统文字和拉丁新文字拼写，标题有误。"},{"pid":"0c2d1480f2dec9be308a96c788f29b9d955b56c4","tid":2060863,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"喳"},{"pid":"43682a8d8f0c054b9a68b76890e3f84fbadb6fea","tid":2060863,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0c2d1480f2dec9be308a96c788f29b9d955b56c4","tid":2060863,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"喳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APdObTO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPdObTO.png&h=99ea3318&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}